sequenceDiagram
    participant Clinician
    participant EHR
    participant CRD as CRD Service<br/>(Phase 5)
    participant DTR as DTR Service<br/>(Questionnaires)
    participant PAS as PAS Service<br/>(Decision Engine)
    participant PAQueue as PA Queue<br/>(Async)
    participant Reviewer as Payer<br/>Reviewer
    participant HAPI as HAPI FHIR<br/>Server

    Clinician->>EHR: Select order (MRI Brain)
    EHR->>CRD: order-select hook<br/>(CDS Hooks)
    CRD->>HAPI: Fetch patient context<br/>(optional)
    CRD->>EHR: Return cards<br/>(PA required, docs needed)
    
    Clinician->>EHR: Click "Start PA"
    EHR->>DTR: GET /api/dtr/Questionnaire/<br/>by-service/70553
    DTR->>EHR: Return Questionnaire
    
    Clinician->>EHR: Fill questionnaire
    EHR->>DTR: POST /api/dtr/Questionnaire/response
    DTR->>HAPI: Store QuestionnaireResponse
    DTR->>EHR: Return responseId
    
    EHR->>PAS: POST /api/pas/PriorAuth/submit<br/>(with responseId, order details)
    PAS->>PAQueue: Enqueue PA request
    PAS->>EHR: Return authId + status=submitted
    
    Note over PAQueue: Async Processing
    PAQueue->>PAS: Pick PA from queue
    PAS->>HAPI: Fetch supporting resources
    PAS->>PAS: Apply decision rules<br/>(auto-approve vs manual)
    
    alt Auto-Approve Path
        PAS->>PAS: Status = approved
    else Manual Review Path
        PAS->>Reviewer: Task assignment<br/>(UM staff worklist)
        Reviewer->>PAS: Review + decision
        PAS->>HAPI: Store reviewer notes
    end
    
    PAS->>EHR: Webhook/push notification<br/>status=approved
    EHR->>Clinician: PA granted! Order can proceed
    Clinician->>EHR: Sign order
    
    Note over EHR,CRD: Back to CRD for final check
    EHR->>CRD: order-sign hook
    CRD->>EHR: Return cards (PA resolved)
    
    Clinician->>EHR: Submit for execution
    EHR->>HAPI: Create order in system